00:24:28.100 --> 00:24:29.840 align:middle line:84%
And that's great, because
it gives our mind something

00:24:29.840 --> 00:24:30.520 align:middle line:90%
to grab onto.

00:24:30.520 --> 00:24:34.380 align:middle line:84%
But yes, it increases--
there's like 14

00:24:34.380 --> 00:24:37.800 align:middle line:84%
different medical
benefits from meditating,

00:24:37.800 --> 00:24:41.630 align:middle line:84%
including the release
