00:24:41.630 --> 00:24:43.940 align:middle line:84%
It reduces cortisol and
the effects of cortisol

00:24:43.940 --> 00:24:47.530 align:middle line:84%
in the body, increases immunity
and enhances the immune system,

00:24:47.530 --> 00:24:48.837 align:middle line:90%
improves the relationships.

00:24:48.837 --> 00:24:50.170 align:middle line:90%
It's all those wonderful things.

00:24:50.170 --> 00:24:52.500 align:middle line:84%
>>DAVIDJI: And that recent
University of Massachusetts

00:24:52.500 --> 00:24:55.930 align:middle line:84%
Mass General study proved
that meditation actually

00:24:55.930 --> 00:24:58.460 align:middle line:84%
changes the physical
structure of your brain.

00:24:58.460 --> 00:25:01.100 align:middle line:84%
