anger, your fear, your stress

00:25:16.490 --> 00:25:17.640 align:middle line:90%
area.

00:25:17.640 --> 00:25:19.630 align:middle line:90%
So let's do that.

00:25:19.630 --> 00:25:20.780 align:middle line:90%
Let's shrink our amygdala.

00:25:20.780 --> 00:25:23.900 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Increases
tolerance and patience,

00:25:23.900 --> 00:25:26.030 align:middle line:84%
which every parent
