>>DAVIDJI: Well, the heart
is a beautiful place.

00:25:58.780 --> 00:26:01.100 align:middle line:84%
There are many ways
that we can connect

00:26:01.100 --> 00:26:04.100 align:middle line:90%
to heart type meditations.

00:26:04.100 --> 00:26:08.120 align:middle line:84%
And it's one of the things
