00:28:17.346 --> 00:28:18.680 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I don't even drink soda.

00:28:18.680 --> 00:28:20.221 align:middle line:84%
>>DAVIDJI: I don't
drink soda either,

00:28:20.221 --> 00:28:22.290 align:middle line:84%
but I reach for SODA
when I find myself

00:28:22.290 --> 00:28:27.600 align:middle line:84%
in a cartwheel, trampoline,
hair on my jacket moment.

00:28:27.600 --> 00:28:30.140 align:middle line:84%
So any time that moment
occurs, and we all

00:28:30.140 --> 00:28:35.090 align:middle line:84%
have a moment like that once
in a while, reach for SODA.

00:28:35.090 --> 00:28:36.290 align:middle line:90%
S-- stop.

00:28:36.290 --> 00:28:42.530 align:middle line:84%
In that moment, just stop
and take a breath in.

00:28:42.530 --> 00:28:47.150 align:middle line:84%
O, the O in SODA--
observe, witness.

00:28:47.150 --> 00:28:51.790 align:middle line:84%
In that moment, sort of
lift up until it's just

00:28:51.790 --> 00:28:54.670 align:middle line:90%
you and another child of God.

00:28:54.670 --> 00:28:57.180 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes you may have to go
up to the Empire State Building

00:28:57.180 --> 00:28:57.590 align:middle line:90%
height.

00:28:57.590 --> 00:28:59.423 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes you may have
to go up to the moon.

00:28:59.423 --> 00:29:00.529 align:middle line:90%
But just keep going up.

00:29:00.529 --> 00:29:02.320 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes you can just
hover on the ceiling

00:29:02.320 --> 00:29:04.790 align:middle line:84%
and say, ah, two
children of God.

00:29:04.790 --> 00:29:07.100 align:middle line:90%
And D-- detach.

00:29:07.100 --> 00:29:10.170 align:middle line:84%
In that moment, you need to
create a physical as well

00:29:10.170 --> 00:29:13.980 align:middle line:84%
as an energetic space between
you and the cartwheeler,

00:29:13.980 --> 00:29:15.959 align:middle line:90%
or whatever that is.

00:29:15.959 --> 00:29:17.250 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Car accident, whatever.

00:29:17.250 --> 00:29:17.660 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:29:17.660 --> 00:29:18.576 align:middle line:90%
>>DAVIDJI: Absolutely.

00:29:18.576 --> 00:29:20.450 align:middle line:90%
Even if you're reading an email.

00:29:20.450 --> 00:29:24.810 align:middle line:84%
So the detach is you just
taking a deep breath in

00:29:24.810 --> 00:29:27.830 align:middle line:84%
as you physically
move your body back

00:29:27.830 --> 00:29:29.740 align:middle line:90%
a little bit from the situation.

00:29:29.740 --> 00:29:31.800 align:middle line:90%
So just go [BREATHES IN].

00:29:31.800 --> 00:29:33.760 align:middle line:84%
So if you're on the
phone, [BREATHES IN].

00:29:33.760 --> 00:29:35.770 align:middle line:90%
If you're texting.

00:29:35.770 --> 00:29:37.800 align:middle line:84%
If you're typing,
roll your chair back.

00:29:37.800 --> 00:29:39.667 align:middle line:84%
But if you're with
someone, just ease

00:29:39.667 --> 00:29:41.750 align:middle line:84%
yourself back a little
bit, take a deep breath in.

00:29:41.750 --> 00:29:44.100 align:middle line:90%
That's the detach part of that.

00:29:44.100 --> 00:29:46.070 align:middle line:90%
And then A, awaken.

00:29:46.070 --> 00:29:47.640 align:middle line:90%
Awaken to you most divine self.

00:29:47.640 --> 00:29:49.140 align:middle line:90%
Awaken to your best version.

00:29:49.140 --> 00:29:51.730 align:middle line:84%
You would say, how would
the best version of Lisa

00:29:51.730 --> 00:29:53.560 align:middle line:90%
respond in this moment?

00:29:53.560 --> 00:29:56.590 align:middle line:84%
How would the best
version of me respond?

00:29:56.590 --> 00:29:59.610 align:middle line:84%
The best version of
you doesn't bark.

00:29:59.610 --> 00:30:02.310 align:middle line:84%
The best version of you is
loving and leads with love,

00:30:02.310 --> 00:30:05.460 align:middle line:84%
and is magnanimous, and
can handle anything.

00:30:05.460 --> 00:30:07.870 align:middle line:84%
The best version of you is
compassionate and forgives

00:30:07.870 --> 00:30:08.880 align:middle line:90%
instantly.

00:30:08.880 --> 00:30:10.960 align:middle line:84%
The best version of you
turns the other cheek.

00:30:10.960 --> 00:30:13.350 align:middle line:84%
The best version of you
never needs to be right.

00:30:13.350 --> 00:30:15.670 align:middle line:84%
So if you can go through
that-- and we're human.

00:30:15.670 --> 00:30:17.830 align:middle line:84%
So of course, we're going
to try all those things.

00:30:17.830 --> 00:30:23.180 align:middle line:84%
But if we can go stop,
observe, detach, awaken,

00:30:23.180 --> 00:30:25.870 align:middle line:84%
