00:41:31.414 --> 00:41:32.896 align:middle line:90%
earth.

00:41:32.896 --> 00:41:35.860 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:41:35.860 --> 00:42:03.770 align:middle line:90%


00:42:03.770 --> 00:42:07.290 align:middle line:84%
The space tracks, they
flow pure potentiality.

00:42:07.290 --> 00:42:09.160 align:middle line:84%
They're pregnant
with possibilities,

00:42:09.160 --> 00:42:11.756 align:middle line:84%
and we can actually
awaken that within us

00:42:11.756 --> 00:42:15.370 align:middle line:90%
